@startuml
title 应用设置界面功能（精确版）

actor 用户
participant "SettingsActivity" as Activity
participant "SettingsViewModel" as VM
participant "AppPreferences" as Prefs

用户 -> Activity: 打开设置界面
Activity -> Activity: setContent { SettingsScreen }
Activity -> VM: viewModel(factory: Factory)
VM -> Prefs: getApiBaseUrlFlow(dataStore)
Prefs --> VM: Flow<String>
VM --> Activity: StateFlow<String>
用户 -> Activity: 修改 TextField
Activity -> VM: updateApiBaseUrl(newUrl: String)
VM -> Prefs: setApiBaseUrl(dataStore, newUrl)
Prefs --> VM: 无返回值
VM --> Activity: 更新 UI
@enduml